Don't join this tuition because she teaches less and gives homework more. I don't want to give even 1 star but giving for technical mandatory.  She gives less teaching and lots of homework. She enters into personal matters. She leaves us late and doesn't not understand if we have some work.

Thanks for reading and don't join.

The 2 reviews down r given by her itself.  So doesn't deserve 4.4 out of 5.

reviewReply.comment:
I deeply regret that things didn't work out for you.

I have taken your feedback about homework but the mantra for excelling in mathematics is to practice practice and practice!! Along with unique ways of teaching, it is important to solve problems related to that concept regularly to strengthen the understanding of the concept!

I care about my students and always hope the best for them. If there is anything the students want to talk about, I am always available for them. I do not intend to be involved in any personal matters.

The 2 reviews are given by my own children for whom I have taught mathematics and I am proud that they have done well.

My aim as a teacher is to not only to teach the subject mathematics but also to inculcate the moral values through my teaching.
